# Hardhat Configuration
# DO NOT commit .env file to git!
# Use 'npx hardhat vars set' to securely store these values

# Example values - Replace with your own:

# MNEMONIC=your twelve word seed phrase here for wallet access
# INFURA_API_KEY=your_infura_project_id_here
# ETHERSCAN_API_KEY=your_etherscan_api_key_here

# How to get these:
# 1. MNEMONIC: Your wallet's 12-word recovery phrase (NEVER share this!)
# 2. INFURA_API_KEY: Sign up at https://infura.io and create a project
# 3. ETHERSCAN_API_KEY: Sign up at https://etherscan.io/myapikey

# To set these securely:
# npx hardhat vars set MNEMONIC
# npx hardhat vars set INFURA_API_KEY
# npx hardhat vars set ETHERSCAN_API_KEY
